Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.71,0:11:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.31,0:11:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我买了御门家的蛋糕 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.62,0:11:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.47,0:11:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一人一半吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.88,0:11:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.34,0:11:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天怎么样 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.77,0:11:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作…就说操纵Fafner什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没问题 我们超厉害的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.64,0:11:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 美三香真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.14,0:11:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要姐也夸你很勇敢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.57,0:11:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我都不太记得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好像 做梦一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.75,0:11:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常痛 却醒不过来的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.73,0:11:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实真没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.94,0:11:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可却时不时担心会发生什么不好的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.99,0:11:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.20,0:11:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美三香？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.38,0:11:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美三香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等着 妈妈马上放你出来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.97,0:12:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又承蒙款待了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人吃也只会多出来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.31,0:12:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然比不上一骑做的菜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.85,0:12:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且这样真令人怀念起世界和平的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.95,0:12:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子们都平安无事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.21,0:12:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.87,0:12:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们也已是出色的大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.26,0:12:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.57,0:12:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.00,0:13:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把美三香放出来啊 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.93,0:13:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不经机体就发生了SDP
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.67,0:13:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急呼叫龙骨区负责人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.82,0:13:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.94,0:13:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零央？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.19,0:13:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御门同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.58,0:13:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空间跳跃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这究竟是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.59,0:13:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.08,0:13:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是美三香家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.85,0:13:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零央 你是从哪来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.11,0:13:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从我家啊 不知道怎么就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.66,0:13:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.43,0:13:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.31,0:13:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是Fafner放出的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.69,0:13:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 可能是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.08,0:14:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是碰到可怕的事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.99,0:14:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.08,0:14:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思考联系的时候知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.38,0:14:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你或者彗总是最先碰到敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然会害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.95,0:14:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 我是在害怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得 迟早会发生不好的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.75,0:14:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会砍倒所有冲向你的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会陪在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.81,0:14:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 不要哭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.99,0:14:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没哭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.13,0:14:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 这个不能消掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.72,0:14:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…零央来砍掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.42,0:14:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别瞎说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.65,0:15:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美三香…美三香
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.14,0:15:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,—没事吧 有没有哪里痛  —妈妈 好难过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.65,0:15:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,—妈妈担心死了 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.51,0:15:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,—太好了 太好了  —没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.25,0:15:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边也是 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.99,0:15:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 似乎不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.90,0:15:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 保险起见所有人都检查一下为好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.61,0:15:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会洗好再还给您的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.99,0:15:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.76,0:15:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.87,0:15:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再这样就杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.92,0:15:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.25,0:15:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了 起床
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织姬 你要轻点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.68,0:16:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找下一只
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.76,0:16:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.22,0:16:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美三香 这个带上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.45,0:16:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是零央落下的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.59,0:16:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…唔咳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.37,0:16:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零央那孩子不错 又很正经
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.95,0:16:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,个子也很快会长高的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.88,0:16:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.23,0:16:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐喜姐 总是麻烦你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.63,0:16:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客气 反正一直空着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.27,0:16:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人用房子也会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.73,0:16:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.60,0:16:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.58,0:17:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 现在开始驾驶员集训
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.54,0:17:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先请剑司学长致辞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.41,0:17:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都听说了 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.86,0:17:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在平常状态下也发生了驾驶机体时的现象 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.74,0:17:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然检查无异常
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.37,0:17:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果发现彼此有不对劲的地方 要马上通知我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.04,0:17:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.03,0:17:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.88,0:17:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早苗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.68,0:17:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信号确认
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.97,0:17:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是岛上的高速联络机隼风 代号拂晓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.02,0:17:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现开始导航
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.41,0:17:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上是现阶段的报告
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.03,0:17:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变岛的航向
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.15,0:17:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不进行第三次派遣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.47,0:17:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全岛前往迎接他们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.11,0:18:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了 还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.49,0:18:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人数多啊 快来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.13,0:18:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.79,0:18:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起吃饭真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.07,0:18:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你家不是双亲健在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.19,0:18:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总是一个人吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.26,0:18:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸妈都很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.83,0:18:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔早归也一直关在房间里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.05,0:18:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.02,0:18:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐喜姐 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.26,0:18:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派遣部队送来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.37,0:18:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类与星核共存于一处
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.09,0:18:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是一口古井
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.68,0:18:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是艾米莉存放了星核碎片的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.05,0:18:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才 我们与两万幸存者一同出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.72,0:19:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道将是怎样的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.02,0:19:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 我们必将到达希望之地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座岛 真是和平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.17,0:19:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是败给敌人 就会是同样下场
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.43,0:19:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太蠢了 竟然跟人类军一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.81,0:19:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这对岛也有好处
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.06,0:19:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之 幸好大家都平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.78,0:19:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就做自己力所能及的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.80,0:19:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 今天先睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.16,0:19:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零央在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.72,0:19:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 你忘的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.48,0:19:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看了里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.12,0:19:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 里面有东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.68,0:19:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美香三香 女生在2楼 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.27,0:19:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.25,0:19:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.12,0:19:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安 零央
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.02,0:19:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.96,0:19:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还能战斗 回过神来已经在想这事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.11,0:20:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没资格说一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.40,0:20:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然电池都快用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.39,0:20:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在培养后辈们才是我们的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.29,0:20:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.05,0:20:37.04,note3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fs42}驾驶员包场
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.20,0:20:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是轻松啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.52,0:20:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…现在敌人来了好像会输
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.81,0:20:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修行不足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.84,0:20:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在敌人来了绝对会输
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.16,0:20:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.22,0:20:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神准备不够充分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 是会输吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.66,0:21:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.85,0:21:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织姬 你干嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.54,0:21:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是美三香的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.05,0:21:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.46,0:21:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很适合呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.47,0:21:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是美三香的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.13,0:21:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗之后还真精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.98,0:21:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.30,0:21:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近藤老师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.59,0:21:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.84,0:21:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.89,0:21:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里奈学姐啊 在这里睡觉会感冒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.46,0:21:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 里奈学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.12,0:21:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.81,0:21:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同化现象
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.04,0:21:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.81,0:21:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.34,0:21:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要碰任何东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.01,0:22:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里奈学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.00,0:22:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.54,0:22:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为人的外貌 心灵 生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.94,0:22:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要依然希求战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.39,0:22:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会不断失去 你终将知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.16,0:22:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们追求着未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.12,0:22:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丧失之物尽可能少的未来
